  <intervention>
    <intervention_type>Device</intervention_type>
    <intervention_name>Autologous engineered skin substitutes</intervention_name>
    <description>Autologous skin cells combined with a biopolymer sponge which is transplanted to excised, full-thickness burns, excised or incised burn scars, or excised full-thickness congenital giant melanocytic nevus. Repeated administrations until all skin wounds are closed.</description>
